  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "School holidays for one week from tomorrow",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has announced that a holiday has been given to all government and private schools in the country for one week from Monday.",
        "The Ministry of Education has further informed that the decision has been taken due to the fuel crisis in the country.",
        "It is noteworthy that it has been announced that all government and government-recognized private schools nationwide have been given a holiday from tomorrow to the 8th."
      ],
